name: Norman Reedus
description:
Norman Mark Reedus (born January 6, 1969) is an American actor best known for starring as Daryl Dixon in the AMC horror drama series The Walking Dead. He also starred as Murphy MacManus in the film The Boondock Saints and its sequel The Boondock Saints II: All Saints Day, Scud in Marvel's Blade II, Marco in Deuces Wild, and himself in his AMC TV show Ride with Norman Reedus.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

So happy about this one :D Today I present my textual inversion of Norman Reedus. I used 60 public images of him, with a 4700 steps process. Hope you'll like it! To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add norreedus69 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20, and CFG around 7 seems to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Realistic Vision. Face restore could help sometimes, especially when the image is not a close-up/portrait. Check the gallery for some inspiration!
